    "ts": "1698142325.046229",
    "thread_ts": "1694638844.141839",
    "root": {
      "type": "message",
      "text": "Working on my slides for the <https://www.thestrangeloop.com/2023/an-approach-to-computing-and-sustainability-inspired-from-permaculture.html|strange loop talk> right now.\nI'm not sure how relevant to FoC it is, as it's a tiny bit more like.. the past of coding, but I'm pretty excited for it, the slides are encoded in a little slideshow scripting language I made up, for a program(Adelie) written in my favourite language in the world, running on a system built from garbage held together with strings and duct tape! Should be fun : )",
